<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Contraseña restablecida — La Ferretería del Barrio</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1f4f9, #e0e7ff);
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .success-container {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      width: 420px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .success-header img {
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }
    .success-header h3 {
      color: #007bff;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #28a745;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    a:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-container">
    <div class="success-header">
      <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo Ferretería" />
      <h3>La Ferretería del Barrio</h3>
    </div>

    <h2>¡Contraseña actualizada!</h2>
    <p>Tu contraseña ha sido restablecida correctamente.  
    Ya puedes iniciar sesión con tus nuevas credenciales.</p>

    <a href="/login">Iniciar sesión</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
